<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">بَابُ:</span> مَنِ الْعَاقِلَةِ الَّتِي تَغْرَمُ؟<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الشَّافِعِيُّ:</span> وَلَمْ أَعْلَمْ مُخَالِفًا فِي أَنَّ الْعَاقِلَةَ الْعَصَبَةُ وَهُمُ الْقَرَابَةُ مِنْ قِبَلِ الْأَبِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>